Planes loot is usually done 1 of 2 ways in my experiences with those hellish places.<BR>1 If you are with a guild, then they will often award items to those members of the guild that they feel have contributed to the raid in a great way<BR>2 It is randomed off between everyone who can use that item because many things are class specific and no drop<BR>That is how it has been in my experiences in plane raids. feel free to flame me if you feel I am totally incorrect.<P>------------------<BR>Blood is like honey... thick and sweet.
